Re: Kana or Romaji?
by yukamina » Mon 06.16.2008 1:17 pm Learning kana doesn't take very long, and it's not a big obstacle. It's best to learn and use kana from the start, then everything you learn from there will improve your kana abilities. Well, romaji at the very beginning isn't bad, but to use an entire text book in romaji is a bit overboard.
