Re: Kana or Romaji?
by monkeykoder » Mon 06.16.2008 1:50 pm I would try to learn kana as soon as possible they aren't all that hard. Just don't do as my first Japanese class did and take an entire semester to learn all the hiragana and then in the second semester just assume everyone spent their summer learning katakana. It shouldn't take more than a day to have a decent idea of what you're looking at and then you can just look at a reference to figure out the ones you don't know. After a week or so you shouldn't need the reference.
